text: "Wasted" is a song by American singer Carrie Underwood from her debut studio album, Some Hearts (2005). ==Music video== It premiered on CMT on February 15, 2007. The video debuted at number 20 on CMT's Top 20 Countdown for the week of March 15, 2007. The video peaked at number 1 on CMT's Top Twenty Countdown for three consecutive weeks in May 2007. ==References== Category:2005 songs Category:2000s ballads Category:Country ballads Category:Carrie Underwood songs
